wikipedia_page.main: Jamie Reid (born 11 January 1994) is a Scottish professional footballer, who plays for Brechin City as a Winger. Reid has previously played for Dundee, Stenhousemuir, Montrose, Arbroath, Elgin City and Lochee United.
